  "feature_bullets": [
    "Gentler Bath Water for Sensitive Skin – Advanced filtration reduces chlorine & water irritants so your baby’s delicate skin stays soft, soothed, and protected. Perfect for reducing dryness, itchiness and irritation after bath time.",
    "3-in-1 Design for Peace of Mind & Comfort – Doubles as a soft BPA-free silicone spout cover to cushion accidental bumps and a color-changing, battery-free temperature gauge so you always know when water is just right for your little one.",
    "Easy Install, Use & Easy Clean Materials – Install in minutes without tools on most tub spouts. Replace the filter every 90 days to continue enjoying the benefits of cleaner water. Place parts on the top rack of the dishwasher for a deep clean.",
    "Skin-Friendly Water – Cleaner water helps support healthy-looking skin and reduces the chances of redness, dryness, and irritation often caused by unfiltered tap water.",
    "The Canopy Brand Promise - 60 Day Guarantee – We are driven by the quality of our products and our commitment to creating reimagined household devices that effortlessly optimize the home for beauty and wellness. Every Tub Filter comes with our state of the art technology and design - an experience only found with Canopy."
  ],
  "feature_bullets_count": 5,
  "feature_bullets_flat": "The Canopy Brand Promise - 60 Day Guarantee – We are driven by the quality of our products and our commitment to creating reimagined household devices that effortlessly optimize the home for beauty and wellness. Every Tub Filter comes with our state of the art technology and design - an experience only found with Canopy. Skin-Friendly Water – Cleaner water helps support healthy-looking skin and reduces the chances of redness, dryness, and irritation often caused by unfiltered tap water. Easy Install, Use & Easy Clean Materials – Install in minutes without tools on most tub spouts. Replace the filter every 90 days to continue enjoying the benefits of cleaner water. Place parts on the top rack of the dishwasher for a deep clean. 3-in-1 Design for Peace of Mind & Comfort – Doubles as a soft BPA-free silicone spout cover to cushion accidental bumps and a color-changing, battery-free temperature gauge so you always know when water is just right for your little one. Gentler Bath Water for Sensitive Skin – Advanced filtration reduces chlorine & water irritants so your baby’s delicate skin stays soft, soothed, and protected. Perfect for reducing dryness, itchiness and irritation after bath time.",
